<style>
  .panel-container {
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 2;
    width: 50;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    /* Aged-wood / parchment palette to match the colonial settlement. */
    background-color: #2a2018;
    border-color: #5b4226;
    border-width: 0.15;
    border-radius: 3;
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 4;
    font-weight: medium;
    color: #f4ead2;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .sub-heading {
    font-size: 2;
    color: #cbb78f;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 0.3;
  }

  /* Plain-language controls so a player knows how to move + turn. */
  .controls-hint {
    font-size: 1.7;
    font-weight: medium;
    color: #e0c074;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 1.2;
    background-color: #3a2e22;
    border-radius: 1;
    padding: 1;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Small caption that labels which control scheme the hint below is for. */
  .controls-title {
    font-size: 1.5;
    font-weight: medium;
    color: #cbb78f;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 0.05;
  }

  /* Primary call to action: begins the arrival orientation cinematic. */
  #enter-colony {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1.5;
    margin-top: 2;
    background-color: #c79a4b;
    color: #2a2018;
    border-radius: 1.5;
    border-width: 0.1;
    border-color: #e0c074;
    font-size: 2.5;
    font-weight: medium;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>
<div id="welcome-root" class="panel-container">
  <span class="heading"> Virginia Ventures, 1620 </span>
  <span class="sub-heading"> You've crossed the Atlantic to a new colony. Plant to feed your people, trade for wealth, and keep the Crown's favor as the settlement weathers four seasons. Every choice has a cost - prosperity is a balance.</span>
  <span class="controls-title">Move in Desktop Mode</span>
  <span class="controls-hint">Move: W A S D keys  -  Turn: Left / Right arrow keys  -  Click anyone with a gold ring to talk or trade.</span>
  <span class="controls-title">Move in VR Headset Mode</span>
  <span class="controls-hint">Move: Left thumbstick  -  Turn: Right thumbstick  -  Point a controller and pull the trigger to talk or trade.</span>
  <span class="controls-title">Too much on screen?</span>
  <span class="controls-hint">Press "Hide Panels" on the bar at the bottom to tuck your scoreboard and lists away. Press it again to bring them back. (Shortcut: B button in VR, H key on desktop.)</span>
  <button id="enter-colony">Enter the Colony</button>
</div>
